rComments: The class is very difficult, most of your grade comes from the Lab Reports that the TA grades and he grades very tough and very opinion based. He is not helpful at all and the experiments are pointless. The exams are hard in that the professor grades them very strictly. There is a group project in the end which almost 40$ of your grade.
This lab class is very difficult and the lecture is very boring. He is a nice guy, but the class is tough. No textbook.

Took for Advanced Topics in Psych: Language Comp. No text book, readings are all psychology journals which are not for the layman. Tests are all essay (3 per test, 2 tests per semester) and cover EVERYTHING. This class is EXTREMELY difficult -if you are AVI student needing a 400 level psych class, avoid this one. He is helpful but its just hard!
